### ============================================================================
### TRANSCRIPTION CONTROLLER (Result Management)
### ============================================================================

### 5. Get all transcriptions for a specific user (KeycloakId)
GET {{host}}/transcriptions/user/{{keycloakId}}
Accept: application/json

### 6. Get details of a single transcription by ID (Long)
# Change '1' to an ID that actually exists in your DB
GET {{host}}/transcriptions/1
Accept: application/json

### 7. Delete transcription by ID
DELETE {{host}}/transcriptions/1
Accept: application/json

### 8. Get all transcriptions in the system (Admin check)
GET {{host}}/test/get-all
Accept: application/json